{"data":{"title":"分心不是我的错","description":"","date":"2026-04-06T22:20:54.000Z","updated":"2026-04-07T06:20:54.139Z","language":"zh-CN","comments":false,"url":"reading/distriction/index.html","cover":null,"images":[],"content":"<html><head></head><body><blockquote>\n<p>共 10 条摘录，最近更新：2026-03-27</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"zhaizhai-masonry zhaizhai-reading-detail\">\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-03-27</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">语言问题可以有各种形态和各种程度。<br>孩子也许是听不懂，<br>也许是表达不出来。<br>听不懂的孩子在表达上也会有困难，<br>因为要先听懂了，<br>才能知道要表达什么。<br>表达不出来的孩子在说或写方面会有困难，<br>也可能在理解能力上会有困难。</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《分心不是我的错》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-03-27</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">注意力缺失症的原发性和次发性症状不同。<br>原发性症状指的是注意力缺失症本来有的症状：分心、冲动、静不下来。<br>次发性症状是最难治疗的，<br>它是注意力缺失症而引起的连锁反应：自我形象低落、沮丧、无聊、挫折、惧怕学习新事物、人际关系不好、滥用药物或酗酒、偷窃，<br>甚至因为长期的挫折而有暴力行为</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《分心不是我的错》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-03-27</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">在个别治疗时，<br>孩子可能和治疗师坐在一起并快乐地玩游戏，<br>所有平日在家里和学校里发生的有问题的行为都不见了。<br>在团体治疗时，<br>这些有问题的行为又会出现，<br>并可以现场处理并教导</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《分心不是我的错》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-03-27</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">阅读障碍儿童或注意力缺失症儿童也许会跌跌撞撞，<br>也许会和文字、书本或其他人脱离，<br>但是他也可能会大放异彩。<br>他可能用新的、令人意外的方式连接事情，<br>他以他的方式发现新的美好事物。<br>所以我们必须保持这些孩子的心灵之窗干干净净，<br>不要受到羞辱、批评、失败和自我价值低落的污染</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《分心不是我的错》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-03-27</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">合理而明显的焦虑是指一个人习惯性忘记自己的责任、做白日梦、言行冲动、迟到以及迟交作业等，<br>这是所有注意力缺失症患者的典型症状</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《分心不是我的错》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-03-27</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">他们宁可协商失败或是过早投降，<br>也要避免挫折。<br>他们宁可违背自己的意愿，<br>也不想再忍受协商的煎熬</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《分心不是我的错》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-03-27</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">对于注意力缺失症家庭而言，<br>协商是很重要的一环，<br>应该越早开始越好，<br>但是不要期待年纪小的孩子能够有效地参与协商</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《分心不是我的错》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-03-27</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">他们越来越焦虑，<br>觉得别人胡说八道的话被当成是有意义的话，<br>害怕全世界的人都对胡说的话信以为真，<br>这是注意力缺失症患者每天面对的挣扎。</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《分心不是我的错》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-03-27</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">分心者也比一般人更有同情心、直觉强、有爱心，<br>似乎在他们那乱七八糟的脑子里，<br>总会特别保留一部分对人或对事的直觉。</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《分心不是我的错》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item x-mood-冷静\">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-tag\">ADHD</span></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-03-27</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">注意力缺失症的迹象随处可见：不稳定、有创造力、爱惹是生非、令人喜爱的个性、动机时有时无、忘东忘西、缺乏组织性、不在乎、成就感低、冲动、追求刺激、不遵守纪律等。</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《分心不是我的错》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span class=\"zhaizhai-loc\">第2章，第44页</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-insight\"><h4>我的理解</h4><div class=\"zhaizhai-back-content\"><p>这段内容提醒我，ADHD 常见表现更应被理解为注意力与执行功能机制问题，而非简单的性格或自律缺陷。</p></div></section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<script>\n(() => {\n  let flipSwitchTimer = null\n\n  document.addEventListener('click', event => {\n    if (event.target.closest('a')) return\n    const card = event.target.closest('.zhaizhai-reading-detail .zhaizhai-flip-card')\n    if (!card) return\n    if (flipSwitchTimer) {\n      clearTimeout(flipSwitchTimer)\n      flipSwitchTimer = null\n    }\n    const container = card.closest('.zhaizhai-reading-detail')\n    const cards = container ? container.querySelectorAll('.zhaizhai-flip-card.is-flipped') : []\n    const isFlipped = card.classList.contains('is-flipped')\n\n    cards.forEach(item => {\n      if (item !== card) item.classList.remove('is-flipped')\n    })\n\n    if (isFlipped) {\n      card.classList.remove('is-flipped')\n    } else {\n      const hasOtherFlipped = [...cards].some(item => item !== card)\n      if (hasOtherFlipped) {\n        // Close previous card first, then open target card for smoother switch.\n        flipSwitchTimer = setTimeout(() => {\n          card.classList.add('is-flipped')\n          flipSwitchTimer = null\n        }, 120)\n      } else {\n        card.classList.add('is-flipped')\n      }\n    }\n  })\n})()\n</script>\n</body></html>","raw":"---\ntitle: 分心不是我的错\ndate: 2026-04-07 06:20:54\ntype: page\naside: true\ncomments: false\n---\n\n> 共 10 条摘录，最近更新：2026-03-27\n\n<div class=\"zhaizhai-masonry zhaizhai-reading-detail\">\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-03-27</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">语言问题可以有各种形态和各种程度。<br>孩子也许是听不懂，<br>也许是表达不出来。<br>听不懂的孩子在表达上也会有困难，<br>因为要先听懂了，<br>才能知道要表达什么。<br>表达不出来的孩子在说或写方面会有困难，<br>也可能在理解能力上会有困难。</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《分心不是我的错》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-03-27</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">注意力缺失症的原发性和次发性症状不同。<br>原发性症状指的是注意力缺失症本来有的症状：分心、冲动、静不下来。<br>次发性症状是最难治疗的，<br>它是注意力缺失症而引起的连锁反应：自我形象低落、沮丧、无聊、挫折、惧怕学习新事物、人际关系不好、滥用药物或酗酒、偷窃，<br>甚至因为长期的挫折而有暴力行为</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《分心不是我的错》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-03-27</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">在个别治疗时，<br>孩子可能和治疗师坐在一起并快乐地玩游戏，<br>所有平日在家里和学校里发生的有问题的行为都不见了。<br>在团体治疗时，<br>这些有问题的行为又会出现，<br>并可以现场处理并教导</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《分心不是我的错》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-03-27</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">阅读障碍儿童或注意力缺失症儿童也许会跌跌撞撞，<br>也许会和文字、书本或其他人脱离，<br>但是他也可能会大放异彩。<br>他可能用新的、令人意外的方式连接事情，<br>他以他的方式发现新的美好事物。<br>所以我们必须保持这些孩子的心灵之窗干干净净，<br>不要受到羞辱、批评、失败和自我价值低落的污染</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《分心不是我的错》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-03-27</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">合理而明显的焦虑是指一个人习惯性忘记自己的责任、做白日梦、言行冲动、迟到以及迟交作业等，<br>这是所有注意力缺失症患者的典型症状</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《分心不是我的错》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-03-27</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">他们宁可协商失败或是过早投降，<br>也要避免挫折。<br>他们宁可违背自己的意愿，<br>也不想再忍受协商的煎熬</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《分心不是我的错》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-03-27</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">对于注意力缺失症家庭而言，<br>协商是很重要的一环，<br>应该越早开始越好，<br>但是不要期待年纪小的孩子能够有效地参与协商</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《分心不是我的错》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-03-27</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">他们越来越焦虑，<br>觉得别人胡说八道的话被当成是有意义的话，<br>害怕全世界的人都对胡说的话信以为真，<br>这是注意力缺失症患者每天面对的挣扎。</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《分心不是我的错》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item \">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-03-27</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">分心者也比一般人更有同情心、直觉强、有爱心，<br>似乎在他们那乱七八糟的脑子里，<br>总会特别保留一部分对人或对事的直觉。</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《分心不是我的错》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span></span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item x-mood-冷静\">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-tag\">ADHD</span></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-03-27</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">注意力缺失症的迹象随处可见：不稳定、有创造力、爱惹是生非、令人喜爱的个性、动机时有时无、忘东忘西、缺乏组织性、不在乎、成就感低、冲动、追求刺激、不遵守纪律等。</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《分心不是我的错》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span class=\"zhaizhai-loc\">第2章，第44页</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-insight\"><h4>我的理解</h4><div class=\"zhaizhai-back-content\"><p>这段内容提醒我，ADHD 常见表现更应被理解为注意力与执行功能机制问题，而非简单的性格或自律缺陷。</p></div></section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<script>\n(() => {\n  let flipSwitchTimer = null\n\n  document.addEventListener('click', event => {\n    if (event.target.closest('a')) return\n    const card = event.target.closest('.zhaizhai-reading-detail .zhaizhai-flip-card')\n    if (!card) return\n    if (flipSwitchTimer) {\n      clearTimeout(flipSwitchTimer)\n      flipSwitchTimer = null\n    }\n    const container = card.closest('.zhaizhai-reading-detail')\n    const cards = container ? container.querySelectorAll('.zhaizhai-flip-card.is-flipped') : []\n    const isFlipped = card.classList.contains('is-flipped')\n\n    cards.forEach(item => {\n      if (item !== card) item.classList.remove('is-flipped')\n    })\n\n    if (isFlipped) {\n      card.classList.remove('is-flipped')\n    } else {\n      const hasOtherFlipped = [...cards].some(item => item !== card)\n      if (hasOtherFlipped) {\n        // Close previous card first, then open target card for smoother switch.\n        flipSwitchTimer = setTimeout(() => {\n          card.classList.add('is-flipped')\n          flipSwitchTimer = null\n        }, 120)\n      } else {\n        card.classList.add('is-flipped')\n      }\n    }\n  })\n})()\n</script>\n"},"api":"api/pages/reading/distriction.json"}